./ ADD NAME=RPFHELP4 0146-20187-23050-2110-00209-00194-00019-Z531415 00
Message:                                 Action:
---------------------------------------  ---------------------------------------
* <ddname> alloc error                *  Archiver: not executed, retry possible
* //* last update nt fnd              *  Add //* last update: ' in record
* //RPFPROF not found                 *  Add //RPFPROF DD-statement
* nnnnnnnn abended ccc                *  Assembler/Linkage editor abended
* xxxxx records cut                   *  EDIT: CUT command executed
* xxxxx records pasted                *  EDIT: PASTE command executed
* xxxxx change(s) made                *  EDIT: Function executed
* xxxxx lines filled                  *  EDIT: FILL command executed
* xxxxx lines xlated                  *  EDIT: UC or LC command executed
* xxxxx members copied/moved          *  MVCPY: successful move/copy (DSN(*))
* xxxxxxxx PENDING                    *  RPF waits for completion linecmds.
* xxxxxxxx Not Found                  *  RPFASM wrong assembler prog. name
* Abend xxx detected                  *  MVCPY: Retry if 913, B0A or x37
* Abend xxx detected                  *  SAVE: Open error, refer to System Codes
* Abendx37 in RPFSAVE                 *  EDIT not exited.
* ACB open err. xxxxxxxx              *  Investigate OPEN error code.
* Access denied                       *  Data entry, Save, dataset functions:
*                                     *  Access rejected by security system.
* Address cannot be altered           *  RPFTEST: address is not altered
* Alloc. error SYSOUT                 *  Command aborted, contact syst.prog.
* Alloc. error workds                 *  Function aborted, contact syst.progr.
* Alloc error xxxx PRINT              *  Edit PRINT and SEARCH,
*                                     *  dataset not allocated
* Allocation error xxxx on dataset    *  Dataset not created (ref. job mngmnt)
* ARCHIVER not installed              *  RPFARCH and RPFARSVE, no ARCHIVER
* Attribute list failed               *  Contact RPF support
* AUTOSAVE not Y or N                 *  DEFAULTS: enter the correct value
* BLK not mult. of LRECL              *  Alloc: not allowed with RECFM=F
* BLKSIZE < 18                        *  Alloc: increase BLKSIZE
* BLKSIZE > 32767                     *  Alloc: decrease BLKSIZE
* Boundaries invalid                  *  Command ignored
* Boundary too small                  *  Command ignored
* BROWSE substituted                  *  If trying to EDIT RECFM=U data
* Cancel 'Yes' or 'No'                *  RPF waits for reply Yes or No
* Change values accepted              *  Function executed
* Chars X'..' found                   *  Successful FIND P'.' subcommand
* Chars 'string' found                *  Successful FIND cmd in Browse
* COL xxx LINE xx.xxx.xxx             *  BROWSE: notify of column and line
* Command name syntx err              *  TSO command ignored
* Command not executed                *  COBOL ON command ignored, RECFM
*                                     *  is variable or LRECL not 80.
* Command not supported               *  TSO command ignored.
* Conflicting commands                *  EDIT: Line commands reset.
* Conflicting DCB Parms               *  MVCPY: Retry menu displayed
* Conflicting line cmds               *  EDIT: Line commands reset.
* Copies invalid                      *  Command aborted
* Copies not numeric                  *  Command aborted
